40:56.414 --> 40:58.041
Ugh.

41:00.752 --> 41:02.212
Ugh.

41:23.525 --> 41:25.985
-How come I feel so dead?
-Don't know, me too.

41:28.154 --> 41:29.114
Yeah.

41:29.155 --> 41:31.199
Captain Sandy?

41:31.241 --> 41:32.867
Sorry, I didn't wanna
call over the radio.

41:32.909 --> 41:35.286
Lloyd's feeling really
tight in the chest.

41:36.996 --> 41:38.957
I just sent him to get
off the deck for a bit.

41:38.998 --> 41:40.375
It started this morning,

41:40.417 --> 41:41.835
and I could just tell
something was up.

41:41.876 --> 41:43.378
He, like, was getting sick

41:43.420 --> 41:45.171
and he just said he was feeing
really tight-chested.

41:45.213 --> 41:47.132
We should take his
blood pressure.

41:51.261 --> 41:53.847
Hi. Drink some water.

41:53.888 --> 41:56.182
Lloyd... where'd he go?

41:56.224 --> 41:58.018
-He's just in his cabin.
-Hey, Lloyd.

41:58.059 --> 42:00.895
I'd like for you to come up
to the bridge.

42:00.937 --> 42:02.313
Do heart problems run
in your family?

42:02.355 --> 42:03.398
No.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.858
Come with me.

42:07.902 --> 42:09.237
Let's take your
blood pressure.

42:09.279 --> 42:12.073
Sit.

42:12.115 --> 42:14.826
I don't know if you know, but I
don't think Lloyd's very well.

42:14.868 --> 42:16.953
Yeah, I do know, thank you.

42:31.509 --> 42:32.969
Is it worse?

42:36.348 --> 42:38.183
I'm gonna have you
lay down after this.

42:44.230 --> 42:45.982
-You're gonna be okay.
-Yeah, I know.

42:46.024 --> 42:47.317
I feel stupid.

42:47.359 --> 42:49.319
Look at me...
you're gonna be fine.

42:49.361 --> 42:50.862
Yeah...

42:50.904 --> 42:52.280
Don't feel stupid.

42:56.451 --> 42:58.203
All right...

43:03.166 --> 43:04.834
You can use my bathroom.

43:08.338 --> 43:09.589
[retches]

43:10.965 --> 43:12.008
He needs to go ashore.

43:12.050 --> 43:13.218
Okay.

43:13.259 --> 43:14.928
Standby.

43:14.969 --> 43:16.471
<i>Malia, Malia, we need</i>
<i>to get Lloyd ashore.</i>

43:16.513 --> 43:18.306
-Copy.
-What happened to Lloyd?

43:18.348 --> 43:20.266
<i>We're gonna do a water taxi.</i>

43:20.308 --> 43:22.018
<i>-Understood.</i>
-Hi, it's Sandy.

43:22.060 --> 43:23.812
I'm sending Lloyd ashore
because his blood pressure

43:23.853 --> 43:25.146
is really high.

43:25.188 --> 43:27.982
He has chest pains, he's
nauseous...

43:28.024 --> 43:29.067
[vomits]

43:29.109 --> 43:31.027
...and I'm concerned.

43:31.069 --> 43:32.028
<i>-Okay.</i>
-Okay.

43:32.070 --> 43:33.071
All right, thank you.

43:33.113 --> 43:34.155
Wait, what happened to Lloyd?

43:36.616 --> 43:38.201
Oh, no, really?

43:38.243 --> 43:40.453
Okay, you're gonna go
to the hospital, right?

43:40.495 --> 43:42.038
Yeah, but you're gonna be fine.

43:42.080 --> 43:43.331
What happened?

43:43.373 --> 43:44.958
Something with
his chest, apparently.

43:45.000 --> 43:47.460
That way.

43:47.502 --> 43:50.130
We're coming to
the swim platform.

43:50.171 --> 43:51.381
He's gonna get in the taxi now.

43:51.423 --> 43:53.341
-All right.
-Wanna go that way?

43:53.383 --> 43:55.218
-Yeah.
-It's easier stairs.

43:58.888 --> 44:00.181
Oh.

44:00.223 --> 44:02.517
<i>Water taxi has arrived</i>
<i>at the aft.</i>

44:02.559 --> 44:04.144
Copy.

44:05.353 --> 44:06.563
-Text me, all right?
-Yeah.

44:06.604 --> 44:08.273
[coughing]
